OL,3,CStar Wars and Gremlins voice actor
OL,4,CMark Dodson dies aged 64
OL,6,FVoice actor Mark Dodson has died aged
OL,7,F64, his agent has said.
OL,9,FDodson was known for playing various
OL,10,Falien roles across the Star Wars
OL,11,Funiverse.
OL,13,FHe first voiced Salacious Crumb, a
OL,14,Fcomedic monkey-like creature who works
OL,15,Ffor his gangster leader Jabba the Hutt
OL,16,F(Kevin Michael Richardson), in 1983
OL,17,Ffilm Star Wars: Return Of The Jedi.
