OL,3,CStar Wars and Gremlins voice actor
OL,4,CMark Dodson dies aged 64
OL,6,FIn a Sunday Instagram post, Stellar
OL,7,FAppearances wrote that Dodson died on
OL,8,FSaturday.
OL,10,FThe statement also said: "Mark worked
OL,11,Fon dozens of movies, video games,
OL,12,Fcommercials and advertisements adding
OL,13,Fhis unique voice and sound to each
OL,14,Fcharacter and script he touched.
OL,16,F"Mark truly loved his fans and enjoyed
OL,17,Fmeeting them at conventions around the
OL,18,Fworld.
